        "custom_html": "<style>\n/* =========================================\n   QUICK SHOP MODAL BACKGROUND FIX\n   ========================================= */\n\n/* overlay behind modal — homepage still visible */\n.fancybox-overlay,\n.fancybox-overlay-fixed,\n.fancybox-bg,\n.fancybox-container,\n.fancybox-is-open {\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18) !important;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(1.5px);\n}\n\n/* structural wrappers MUST be transparent */\n.fancybox-wrap,\n.fancybox-skin,\n.fancybox-inner,\n.fancybox-outer {\n  background: transparent !important;\n  box-shadow: none !important;\n  border: 0 !important;\n}\n\n/* only the actual modal box should be dark */\n.fancybox-content,\n.modal.fancybox-content,\n.product-quickshop__container {\n  background: #090a0c !important;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86) !important;\n  box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) !important;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) !important;\n  border-radius: 14px !important;\n}\n\n/* prevent any inherited black fill */\n.fancybox-stage,\n.fancybox-slide,\n.fancybox-slide--html {\n  background: transparent !important;\n}\n\n/* kill rogue pseudo elements */\n.fancybox-wrap::before,\n.fancybox-wrap::after,\n.fancybox-skin::before,\n.fancybox-skin::after,\n.fancybox-inner::before,\n.fancybox-inner::after {\n  display: none !important;\n  content: none !important;\n}\n</style>"
